    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont really want to go to an er if i can help it... it's so expensive here and i'm just exhausted. it feels more like my heart is racing from the caffeine and the stress of the flight. what if i just take some extra calming meds or try to sleep it off for an hour? do u think it's really that serious?",
