      "content": "magnesium? ok that sounds easier. how much should i actually take tho? i have some supplements here. and honestly it's probably just anxiety... i've had these kinds of feelings before when i'm stressed. do you think it's really worth the rush to a hospital for just a bit of chest tightness?",
